{"article_id":"2XDoI4CKxX9yReEw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A North Carolina congressional district remains the last race still up for grabs in 2018 ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"with the election result tangled in fraud allegations","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"and the outcome potentially resting in the hands of the incoming House Democratic majority .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"The state Board of Elections has declined to certify the tally in the state ' s 9th Congressional District","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"after the initial count showed Republican Mark Harris beating Democrat Dan McCready by 905 votes out of more than 280,000 cast .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"What ' s next is unclear","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"but a familiar culprit is at the center of the dispute","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"- absentee ballots .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"The board collected at least six sworn statements from voters","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"who said","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"people came to their homes","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and urged them to hand over their absentee ballots .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Democrats are crying foul ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that ' s ballot-harvesting , a practice","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"that ' s illegal in the state","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"- though they balked at similar complaints from Republicans across the country in California ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"who saw a number of races flip after 11th-hour floods of absentee ballots .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"There was also an unusually large percentage of absentee ballots from minority voters","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"- a reliable Democratic bloc -","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that were not turned in at the polls in North Carolina .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"More than 40 percent of ballots","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"requested by black voters","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and more than 60 percent of ballots","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"requested by Native American voters","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"were not returned .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"By comparison , just 17 percent of ballots","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"sent to white voters","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"did not make it back to election officials ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"according to The News & Observer in Raleigh .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Several investigations are underway ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"including a district attorney probe in Bladen City","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that initially centered on the 2016 cycle","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"but was expanded","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to include the 2018 election .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"\" Reports indicate a direct connection between the Harris campaign and those","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"committing election fraud","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and suggest a calculated effort","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to illegally undermine our democracy , \"","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"said Democratic National Committee spokesman Enrique Gutierrez .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" If the North Carolina Republican Party believes in the integrity of our elections ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"they won ' t stand in the way of an investigation . \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"In California ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"where third-party collection of absentee ballots is legal ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"the massive canvassing operation is typically spearheaded by labor unions .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The practice is known as ballot harvesting .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Republicans were stunned","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"to see races","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"they thought","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"they ' d won","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"suddenly turn upside down .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"\" California just defies logic to me , \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"House Speaker Paul D. Ryan , Wisconsin Republican , said at a recent event","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"hosted by The Washington Post .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"\" We were only down 26 seats the night of the election ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"and three weeks later , we lost basically every California contested race . \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Republicans find themselves on the opposite side of the issue in North Carolina ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"though national GOP leaders are loathe to defend the Harris campaign .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" It is laughable that with a straight face Democrats are actually calling one race","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that they lose voter fraud","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"but the other one in California just plain ballot harvesting , \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"said Shawn Steel , the National Republican Committeeman from California .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"the type of investigations","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"underway in North Carolina","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"should be opened in California ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"where the millions of absentee ballots flipped scores of Republican seats to Democrat this year .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"\" There ' s a fine line","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"to how much you help a voter vote , \"","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Mr. Steel said .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"\" There ' s a huge opportunity for tremendous mischief . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"While millions voted with absentee ballots in California ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"out of 2.3 million ballots","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"cast in North Carolina ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"only about 100,000 were mail-in ballots .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"There are several scenarios","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"for ultimately picking the next congressman from the 9th District :","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"⦁ The board could call for a special election ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"replaying the last contest with Mr. Harris , Mr. McCready and Libertarian Jeff Scott back on the ballot .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"⦁ The U.S. House ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"which will be under Democrat control as of Jan. 3 ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"could decide who to seat .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"⦁","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"The House also could call for a special election ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"starting the process from scratch with new primaries and potentially new candidates .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Rep. Steny Hoyer , the Maryland Democrat","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"who will be the House majority leader next year ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"said Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that Mr. Harris likely would not be seated","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"until the mess is cleared up .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"\" If there is what appears to be a very substantial question on the integrity of the election ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"clearly we would oppose Mr. Harris being seated","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"until that is resolved , \"","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Mr. Hoyer said","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"he planned to discuss it with Rep. Zoe Lofgren , the California Democrat","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"expected to head the House Administration Committee","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that has the power","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"to investigate the election","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"and call for a new one .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"The moves by the State Election Board came under fire from Mr. Harris and the North Carolina GOP .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Mr. Harris said","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"he welcomed an investigation","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"\" as long as it is fair","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"and focuses on all political parties . \"","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"\" But to date , there is absolutely no public evidence","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that there are enough ballots in question","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"to affect the outcome of this race .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Accordingly , the Board should act immediately","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"to certify the race","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"while continuing to conduct their investigation .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"Anything else is a disservice to the people of the Ninth District , \"","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Democrats countered","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"that the election outcome did not have to be in doubt","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"for voter fraud to invalidate the results .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Adding to the mess , the board ' s Democratic chairman , Andy Penry , resigned last week","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"after his tweets","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"criticizing President Trump","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"came to light .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Gov . Roy Cooper , a Democrat , elevated Vice Chairman Joshua Malcolm , also a Democrat , to lead the board .","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"Gerry F. Cohen , former special counsel to the North Carolina General Assembly","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"who drafted state election laws ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"the state has a history of absentee voter fraud","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"dating back to sheriff ' s races in the 1940s .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"\" But this takes the cake .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"This is at a level","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"that is unbelievable , \"","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Like most states , North Carolina does not allow third-part collection of absentee ballots .","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"Because of its murky election past ,","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"its laws are extremely strict on the matter ,","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"even prohibiting a college student from having their roommate drop the absentee ballot in the mail .","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"\" That ' s how strict our law is ,","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"of course that ' s absurd , \"","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"Mr. Cohen said .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"\" But taking unmarked ballots","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"and filling them out .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"That is different than ballot harvesting","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"- it ' s ballot theft . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":143,"right":280,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":143,"left":0,"right":142,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":280,"left":214,"right":279,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":169,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":147,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":144,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":145,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":168,"left":150,"right":167,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":8,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":9,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":167,"left":155,"right":166,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":12,"right":152,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":13,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"N